MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 1336

DECLARING CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND SITUATED IN QUEZON CITY, CALOOCAN CITY IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF RODRIGUEZ, PROVINCE OF RIZAL, AS THE LA MESA WATERSHED RESERVATION FOR PURPOSES OF PROTECTING AND IMPROVING ITS WATER QUANTITY, QUALITY AND SECURITY.

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and the Metropolitan Waterworks and Sewerage System (MWSS), and pursuant to the power vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby establish as LA MESA WATERSHED RESERVATION , parcels of land situated in Quezon City, Caloocan City in the Municipality of Rodriguez, Province of Rizal, subject to private rights, if there be any, and more particularly described as follows:

